<fr:p>This proposition also applies to simplicial objects in other categories <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathscr {C}]]></fr:tex> apart from that of topological spaces; it suffices that <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathscr {C}]]></fr:tex> satisfy the following:

    <fr:tree
